    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Jellyfish blind box 水母盲盒】 这是一款轻松的放置游戏，你可以购买水母盲箱来饲养你的小水母，随着时间的推移出售它们的成熟体以获得利润，或者将它们留在水箱中供人参观，收取参观费。通过不断的积累财富可以购买更贵的水母盲盒，从而解锁全部水母【目前计划是150种水母，试玩版开放小部分】【水母盲盒分多个价位，不同价位的盲盒开出的水母经济价值不同】 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/62997bab0c3ca6c4f97f3ebc79b1cc7e.poster.avif?t=1766140179\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/62997bab0c3ca6c4f97f3ebc79b1cc7e.webm?t=1766140179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/62997bab0c3ca6c4f97f3ebc79b1cc7e.mp4?t=1766140179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/dc555f78b0f65395185c6df764447198.poster.avif?t=1766140179\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/dc555f78b0f65395185c6df764447198.webm?t=1766140179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/dc555f78b0f65395185c6df764447198.mp4?t=1766140179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/3a38cdf4e6740eb652d363fdc937e176.poster.avif?t=1766140179\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069070/extras/3a38cdf4e6740eb652d363fdc937e176.webm?t=1766140179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass